Field.ElementPreceedingHeader: Human Infection with 2019 Novel Coronavirus Person Under Investigation (PUI) and Case Report Form

Field.ElementLabel:
Contact ID
Only complete if case-patient is a known contact of prior source case-patient. Assign Contact ID using CDC 2019-nCoV ID and sequential contact ID, e.g., Confirmed case CA102034567 has contacts CA102034567-01 and CA102034567-02

NNDSS loc. rec. ID/Case ID
For NNDSS reporters, use GenV2 or NETSS patient identifier
What is the current status of this person?

ElementEnum.RawValue:
1, PUI testing pending* 
 2, PUI, tested negative* 
 3, Presumptive case (positive local test), confirmatory testing pending** 
 4, Presumptive case (positive local test), confirmatory tested negative** 
 5, Laboratory-confirmed case** </br>*Testing performed by state, local, or CDC lab.</br>**At this time, all confirmatory testing occurs at CDC

Field.ElementLabel: Report date of PUI to CDC
Report date of case to CDC

Age
Please give age in either: -years (most common) -months -days
You will pick the age unit in the next question.

Age units
The number you gave above was in what units?
Date of first positive specimen collection
Did the patient have acute respiratory distress syndrome?
Did the patient have another diagnosis/etiology for their illness?
Did the patient have an abnormal chest x-ray?
Symptoms present during the course of illness
If symptomatic, date of symptom resolution

ElementEnum.RawValue: 1, Still symptomatic \n 0, Symptoms resolved, unknown date \n 9, Unknown symptom status

Field.ElementLabel: Was the patient admitted to an intensive care unit (ICU)?
Did the patient receive mechanical ventilation (MV)/intubation?
If yes, total days with MV (days)
Did the patient receive extracorporeal membrane oxygenation (ECMO)?
Did the patient die as a result of this illness?
Is the patient a health care worker in the United States?
Does the patient have a history of being in a healthcare facility (as a patient, worker or visitor) in China?

Field.ElementPreceedingHeader: In the 14 days prior to illness onset, did the patient have any of the following exposures (check all that apply):

Field.ElementLabel: Household contact with another lab-confirmed COVID-19 case-patient
Community contact with another lab-confirmed COVID-19 case-patient
Any healthcare contact with another lab-confirmed COVID-19 case-patient
Healthcare contact with another lab-confirmed COVID-19 case-patient -- patient
Healthcare contact with another lab-confirmed COVID-19 case-patient -- visitor
Healthcare contact with another lab-confirmed COVID-19 case-patient -- healthcare worker
Exposure to a cluster of patients with severe acute lower respiratory distress of unknown etiology
If travel to other non-US country, specify
If the patient had contact with another COVID-19 case, was this person a U.S. case?
If yes, specify nCoV ID of source case
